This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-cip-kernel layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  Under AGL UCB 16 (Prickly Pike).

Patches or Issues
=======

- Please submit any patches or issues against the meta-cip-kernel layer on the github,
  Not to mail AGL mailing lists.

Table of Contents
=================

  I. Adding the meta-cip-kernel layer to your build
 II. Misc

I. Adding the meta-cip-kernel layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-cip-kernel' within AGL build environment.

II. Misc
========

Add the following line in conf/local.conf of the build directory if you use AMD GPU.

```
MACHINE_EXTRA_RRECOMMENDS:append = "linux-firmware-amdgpu"
```
